1
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:55,340
Did you sleep well?

2
00:00:58,140 --> 00:00:58,979
No.

3
00:01:00,940 --> 00:01:01,940
Where is Qi?

4
00:01:02,379 --> 00:01:03,140
I'll go find her.

5
00:01:03,459 --> 00:01:04,099
Lie down.

6
00:01:05,060 --> 00:01:05,819
She's in the next room,

7
00:01:05,819 --> 00:01:06,619
sleeping soundly.

8
00:01:06,899 --> 00:01:07,459
Don't disturb her.

9
00:01:08,140 --> 00:01:09,420
There were underhanded tactics on the blade,

10
00:01:09,979 --> 00:01:10,940
which is why you fainted.

11
00:01:13,060 --> 00:01:14,500
I thought I lost the fight.

12
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:16,940
Change the medicine quickly.

13
00:01:32,420 --> 00:01:33,819
Fortunately, the doctor came in time.

14
00:01:34,060 --> 00:01:35,019
I've asked about the situation.

15
00:01:35,459 --> 00:01:36,660
It's not a big problem with proper treatment.

16
00:01:37,819 --> 00:01:39,340
Why were you there yesterday?

17
00:01:44,459 --> 00:01:45,099
Anyway,

18
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:47,340
you two should recover first.

19
00:01:47,979 --> 00:01:49,099
You're absolutely safe with me.

20
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:50,300
We'll deal with

21
00:01:50,940 --> 00:01:51,859
the rest later.

22
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:02,220
Tell me.

23
00:02:04,379 --> 00:02:05,780
The hospital is surrounded by 3Z.

24
00:02:05,979 --> 00:02:07,539
They've also surrounded the dock.

25
00:02:09,340 --> 00:02:10,859
Try to find another way.

26
00:02:11,699 --> 00:02:12,859
They've occupied

27
00:02:12,859 --> 00:02:13,660
all the key routes.

28
00:02:14,139 --> 00:02:15,099
I'll think of another way.

29
00:02:18,139 --> 00:02:19,620
If not, you can contact...

30
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:20,379
I have an idea.

31
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:33,620
Don't worry. I'll help you.

32
00:02:35,940 --> 00:02:37,460
He was badly injured and carrying a blind girl.

33
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:38,979
How could he run far away?

34
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:41,579
Check every hospital.

35
00:02:41,579 --> 00:02:43,900
Turn over every hospital.

36
00:02:45,060 --> 00:02:46,780
Turn over the whole city,

37
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:48,340
if necessary, to catch them.

38
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:53,940
With ASO's ability,

39
00:02:53,940 --> 00:02:55,180
Jiang Yue can't escape.

40
00:02:57,020 --> 00:02:57,539
Gao Qiao,

41
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:00,379
you did it, didn't you?

42
00:03:02,699 --> 00:03:03,259
Sir,

43
00:03:05,660 --> 00:03:06,460
I didn't.

44
00:03:12,859 --> 00:03:14,060
Qi Qi can't see anymore, right?

45
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:15,220
Didn't I tell you to wait at home?

46
00:03:16,299 --> 00:03:17,259
Where's my daughter?

47
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:18,379
Take me to see her.

48
00:03:18,379 --> 00:03:19,379
Listen carefully,

49
00:03:20,660 --> 00:03:22,819
I told you to wait at home.

50
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:25,220
My daughter can't see anymore.

51
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:27,500
If it can't be cured, it'll be a lifelong disability.

52
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,139
Shut up!

53
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:31,579
I married you because you were obedient.

54
00:03:32,740 --> 00:03:34,900
You should stay at home and be Mrs. Jiang.

55
00:03:36,579 --> 00:03:37,379
Take her back.

56
00:03:52,979 --> 00:03:53,460
Mrs. Jiang,

57
00:03:54,660 --> 00:03:56,460
the exhibition cost a lot of money.

58
00:03:57,419 --> 00:03:58,500
Things are complicated now.

59
00:03:59,140 --> 00:03:59,979
So Mr. Jiang...

60
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:02,020
Please understand.

61
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:04,460
I want to see my daughter.

62
00:04:06,299 --> 00:04:07,619
Master is with Miss.

63
00:04:08,380 --> 00:04:09,499
you can rest assured.

64
00:04:12,780 --> 00:04:13,340
I...

65
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:15,220
I want to call Yue'er.

66
00:04:16,179 --> 00:04:16,580
Ma'am,

67
00:04:18,220 --> 00:04:19,739
you'd better not know where they are.

68
00:04:33,220 --> 00:04:34,260
I'll have someone take you back.

69
00:04:39,419 --> 00:04:39,739
Please.

70
00:04:59,979 --> 00:05:00,939
Besides the 3Z exhibition,

71
00:05:02,660 --> 00:05:04,539
you must have promised Lu Qi something else.

72
00:05:06,619 --> 00:05:07,460
Otherwise, she wouldn't have

73
00:05:07,460 --> 00:05:08,900
given up on meeting Müller with me.

74
00:05:11,900 --> 00:05:13,700
Tell me, what is it?

75
00:05:16,499 --> 00:05:17,700
You measure people's emotions

76
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:19,059
with value.

77
00:05:19,660 --> 00:05:21,260
It's right and realistic.

78
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:23,660
But you chose the wrong person.

79
00:05:24,739 --> 00:05:25,780
Qi and I

80
00:05:26,739 --> 00:05:27,700
are in love.

81
00:05:29,059 --> 00:05:29,900
Love.

82
00:05:33,979 --> 00:05:34,419
Love.

83
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:48,939
You are actually a cool guy.

84
00:05:50,260 --> 00:05:51,900
But when you met Lu Qi,

85
00:05:52,700 --> 00:05:53,820
you'll be panic.

86
00:05:55,099 --> 00:05:57,140
All your judgment and rationality will be gone.

87
00:05:58,580 --> 00:05:59,340
One step wrong,

88
00:06:00,460 --> 00:06:01,179
every step wrong.

89
00:06:02,340 --> 00:06:03,340
Even Lu Qi

90
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:06,020
has to pay for your love.

91
00:06:08,739 --> 00:06:10,220
Love is not a good thing.

92
00:06:13,179 --> 00:06:14,340
Our values are different.

93
00:06:14,900 --> 00:06:15,539
We can't be friends.

94
00:06:16,499 --> 00:06:18,700
Birds of a feather flock together.

95
00:06:19,099 --> 00:06:19,499
Jiang Yue,

96
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,460
what if I have something you need?

97
00:06:25,979 --> 00:06:27,299
I'm not a person who likes to beat around the bush.

98
00:06:27,820 --> 00:06:28,780
Just say it.

99
00:06:34,020 --> 00:06:36,099
As a human weapon raised by Jiang Changfa,

100
00:06:37,499 --> 00:06:38,900
I know clearly

101
00:06:39,419 --> 00:06:40,580
why you are like a marionette

102
00:06:40,580 --> 00:06:41,619
at his mercy.

103
00:06:43,059 --> 00:06:43,979
What he gave you

104
00:06:45,299 --> 00:06:46,820
is just a hypothetical enemy, Black Snow.

105
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:49,900
But I

106
00:06:50,739 --> 00:06:52,340
can help you find the real enemy.

107
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:54,939
Go on.

108
00:06:57,900 --> 00:06:58,700
As you said just now,

109
00:07:00,619 --> 00:07:00,859
interest

110
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:02,859
is the standard I use to measure

111
00:07:02,859 --> 00:07:03,660
the relationship between people.

112
00:07:05,820 --> 00:07:06,539
I can tell you,

113
00:07:07,939 --> 00:07:09,340
but what can you offer me in return?

114
00:07:15,380 --> 00:07:15,900
Chumo,

115
00:07:16,499 --> 00:07:17,580
Actually,

116
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:18,739
you are quite impressive,

117
00:07:19,499 --> 00:07:22,299
especially in the field of persuading people.

118
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:23,660
You are the best

119
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:25,660
in this field.

120
00:07:27,419 --> 00:07:27,979
But

121
00:07:28,419 --> 00:07:30,340
there is basically no trust between us.

122
00:07:32,179 --> 00:07:32,979
Don't worry.

123
00:07:33,299 --> 00:07:34,900
It's just a matter of time for the eyes to recover.

124
00:07:35,619 --> 00:07:36,260
I'll go first.

125
00:07:56,739 --> 00:07:57,059
Take the medicine.

126
00:08:18,939 --> 00:08:19,380
Do you want to eat?

127
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:21,819
No.

128
00:08:27,699 --> 00:08:28,539
It's for two people.

129
00:08:28,539 --> 00:08:29,500
I can't finish it.

130
00:08:29,860 --> 00:08:31,539
You're a big eater.

131
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:32,419
You can finish it.

132
00:08:33,179 --> 00:08:34,179
What if I'm too full?

133
00:08:34,620 --> 00:08:35,579
I'll bury you there.

134
00:08:52,219 --> 00:08:53,020
Are you done?

135
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:02,140
Jiang Yue.

136
00:09:03,939 --> 00:09:04,260
Have a drink.

137
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:11,380
Qi.

138
00:09:12,219 --> 00:09:12,780
Where are you hurt?

139
00:09:13,219 --> 00:09:13,660
Are you okay?

140
00:09:14,539 --> 00:09:15,140
I'm fine.

141
00:09:16,299 --> 00:09:17,660
I just want to walk around.

142
00:09:17,660 --> 00:09:19,020
You can call me if you want to walk around.

143
00:09:30,539 --> 00:09:32,140
Qi, we meet again.

144
00:09:33,579 --> 00:09:34,459
Why is he here?

145
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:35,939
Jiang Yue, let's go.

146
00:09:35,939 --> 00:09:36,740
He's dangerous.

147
00:09:37,419 --> 00:09:38,059
Leave now.

148
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:43,059
I'm still worried.

149
00:09:43,740 --> 00:09:44,819
His target is not me.

150
00:09:45,380 --> 00:09:46,900
Then why are we in his house?

151
00:09:47,419 --> 00:09:48,860
Because I can find a good doctor.

152
00:09:50,219 --> 00:09:51,219
Can you go further away?

153
00:09:57,260 --> 00:09:58,699
I've read his case analysis.

154
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:01,900
He likes to manipulate and play.

155
00:10:03,579 --> 00:10:06,459
Use what the prey likes to lure him.

156
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:07,939
He enjoys the process.

157
00:10:09,100 --> 00:10:10,219
You mean

158
00:10:10,939 --> 00:10:13,260
we are the fish he wants to catch.

159
00:10:13,939 --> 00:10:15,819
Before we become his lunch,

160
00:10:16,539 --> 00:10:17,539
he wants to protect us

161
00:10:18,299 --> 00:10:19,740
from being attacked by others.

162
00:10:21,299 --> 00:10:22,939
You're right.

163
00:10:26,860 --> 00:10:27,980
How did you get hurt?

164
00:10:28,459 --> 00:10:29,459
Are you hurt anywhere else?

165
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:31,100
Are you okay?

166
00:10:31,419 --> 00:10:32,179
I'm fine.

167
00:10:33,459 --> 00:10:33,939
It's time to eat.

168
00:10:41,260 --> 00:10:42,059
After Bell died,

169
00:10:42,299 --> 00:10:43,620
his wife and daughter also disappeared.

170
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:44,900
No news till now.

171
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:47,459
What about the totem?

172
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,459
No clue has been found yet.

173
00:10:56,500 --> 00:10:57,500
Andrew Bell,

174
00:11:00,339 --> 00:11:01,819
you really like climbing the wall.

175
00:11:03,020 --> 00:11:03,860
This is my house.

176
00:11:04,579 --> 00:11:05,500
I can go wherever I want.

177
00:11:10,380 --> 00:11:11,260
Do you know this person?

178
00:11:11,819 --> 00:11:13,100
I don't know that unlucky guy.

179
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:15,260
All I know is that

180
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:16,900
he painted something he shouldn't have,

181
00:11:17,699 --> 00:11:18,819
or his family wouldn't have been affected.

182
00:11:20,179 --> 00:11:21,140
You also know about totems?

183
00:11:23,219 --> 00:11:24,100
What doesn't a butterfly know?

184
00:11:26,459 --> 00:11:27,339
If I want to know,

185
00:11:28,579 --> 00:11:29,780
what do I need to exchange?

186
00:11:30,219 --> 00:11:31,819
A butterfly can tell a friend everything.

187
00:11:32,819 --> 00:11:34,299
But you're not my friend yet.

188
00:11:35,299 --> 00:11:36,100
Qi Qi can do that.

189
00:11:37,419 --> 00:11:38,380
But she seems

190
00:11:38,699 --> 00:11:39,900
to be ignoring me.

191
00:11:41,299 --> 00:11:42,980
Because she knows you're a butterfly.

192
00:11:43,579 --> 00:11:44,179
So what?

193
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:46,219
I never intended to hide it from her.

194
00:11:53,260 --> 00:11:53,539
Watch out.

195
00:11:58,020 --> 00:11:58,699
Why are you getting off?

196
00:12:00,819 --> 00:12:02,299
I want to go out for a walk.

197
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:03,299
Where do you want to go?

198
00:12:04,179 --> 00:12:05,939
To the park outside.

199
00:12:06,459 --> 00:12:07,140
Let's go together.

200
00:12:14,059 --> 00:12:15,059
You two stay here.

201
00:12:15,579 --> 00:12:16,539
I'll go buy you some tasty food.
